You can regain that great feeling of confidence you had years ago when a full head of hair was something you took for granted!Easy to Apply: -Nanogen Fibres are applied quickly and without mess by simply shaking the unique container over thin or thinning hair. Nanogen Fibres can also be used before hair transplants to subtly build up the appearance of thicker hair so the transplants don’t cause an obvious and sudden change. These innovations intensify the hair thickening effect created by Nanogen Fibres. Nanogen Fibres have been independently proven to create unrivalled hair density you can really see. The Nanogen Fibres jar also has fill-level windows to indicate when you are running low, to ensure you never run out.100% Safe for Male and Female Thinning Hair :- Over 1 million incredible transformations prove that Nanogen Fibres are safe. They are completely natural and they will not damage your hair or scalp. That’s why they are used by leading hair transplant surgeons to conceal thinning hair right up to surgery, and afterwards to hide the healing wounds. Nanogen Fibres are recommended by the Alopecia Society for men and women with thinning hair. For Male and Female Thinning Hair :- Every Nanogen product is formulated specifically to be gentle on male and female thinning hair whilst maintaining efficacy. Nanogen Fibre Locking Spray is specially formulated not to affect penetration of Minoxidil or any other topical treatment. Complete Hair Camouflage:- Combine Nanogen Conceal & Style products to thicken any area of thinning hair. Apply and blend in Nanogen Fibres for real hair density. Secure them in place all day with Nanogen Fibre Locking Spray. Title: Fragrance And Fashion Boss Eau de Toilette  -  135 ml(For Boys)
Description: Boss is a Aromatic Green fragrance. Hugo is a multi-dimensional fragrance that evokes a sensation of northern air, deep rich forests, and surf crashing against a rugged coastline. The nose behind this fragrance is Bob Aliano. Hugo is classified as a refreshing, spicy, lavender, amber fragrance. This fragrance possesses a blend of woods, fresh citrus and spicy leaves and is uniquely clean and crisp that is as innovative as the guy who wears it.

Title: Playboy Miami EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Fun, frolic and freshness - Miami from Playboy is a fragrance that epitomises all that the vibrant city of Miami is. With this Eau de Toilette, Playboy welcomes you into a life of sunny beaches, beautiful babes, slick clubs, fashionable yachts and plenty of parties. Suave and sensual, Miami is the scent of the free-spirited playboy, who stops at nothing to get what he wants. Passionate and playful, he is the real pleasure-seeker. Opening with a pleasant top note of bergamot, refreshing, leafy, green apple and a hint of ozone, this luxurious scent trails into a heart note of rosewood, jasmine and cyclamen. This is followed by a warm base note of velvety musk, amber and cedar wood, which imparts a magnetic charm to the overall aroma. Encased in a dark, cylindrical flacon with the Playboy bunny embossed on it, Miami is a fragrance for the man who plays hard and wins.

Title: Boss Pure EDT  -  75 ml(For Men)
Description: For the nonchalant man who flaunts his charm with every stride, Boss Pure Eau de Toilette uplifts his sensuality and makes him stand out in the crowd. Aquatic and Woody The irresistible aquatic and woody aroma creates its magic and elevates his mood when he wears this perfume. The contemporary man will lose himself in the whiff of this refined and elegant fragrance that stays longer.

Title: Sapil Disclosure White Eau de Toilette  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Disclosure is a fragrance that blends masculine style with classic luxury. Disclosure fuses woody, spicy and floral fragrances achieving a peak that is both intense and seductive. A rare combination of bright enthusiasm in fresh light floral tones and the sensuality of woody and amber accents that lies in contrast to the balsamic notes make this a masculine mix of classic and pop genres.

Title: Hugo Boss Baldessarini EDC  -  75 ml(For Men)
Description: According to the slogan of the brand?Baldessarini: Separates the men from the boys or in other words,?Baldessarini?s perfumes are aimed at more adult audience.?Baldessarini?is composed of metal, sensual accords which blend with a fresh, spicy composition. The face for this?perfume?is Charles Schumann, the owner of the famous Munich bar. This fragrance for real men awakens fantasy, a wish for travelling to distant, exotic countries. In the beginning you can feel a sharp freshness of orange, mandarin and mint, which hide a special masculine metal note in themselves. The spicy heart is composed of patchouli flower, cumin and cloves. The warm and elegant base is composed of sandalwood, spruce, patchouli leaves, tobacco, ambergris and musk.

Title: Jaguar Amber EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: An oriental fougere for men Fregrans Crisp, Warm, Confident, masculine and sensual

Title: Brut Musk EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Refreshing and oriental, Brut Musk for men is irresistibly masculine. The Brut man stands out for his sensuality and self-confidence. Classy and elegant, he captivates with his enigmatic persona. Powerfully male, he is defined by an equally powerfully essence. An intermingling of the top and heart notes of this fragrance brings together hints of lavender, citrus and geranium, creating a fresh, sweet and spicy accord. A warm base of woody, musky moss adds a touch of sophistication to the overall scent. Perfect for the romantic date in winter, Brut Musk is what real men smell like.

Title: Jovan Colognia EDT  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: MADE IN U.S,A. 100% AUTHENTIC AND ORIGINAL JOVAN MUSK FOR WOMEN`S Experience the sexy feeling of jovan musk women`s- this mysterious fragrance unleashes your own natural powers of seduction. It`s what attracts. Jovan Musk Perfume for women by Jovan, It is designed by the house of jovan in 1972, jovan musk is classified as a luxurious, gentle, floral fragrance. This feminine scent possesses a blend of light musk and delicate florals. It is recommended for romantic wear. All products are original, authentic name brands. This women's fragrance is recommended for daytime wear. 3.25fl oz- 96ml
